songs.title: Polkadots
songs.lyrics:
[Instrumental]
Ten, Nine, Eight, Seven, Six, Five, Four, Three, Two
Are you ready?
We should all wear polkadots
We should all wear polkadots
We should all wear polkadots
We should all wear polkadots
Ten, Nine, Eight, Seven, Six, Five, Four, Three, Two
Are you ready?
We should all wear polkadots
We should all wear polkadots
